::Spears::

She laughed at Striker while pinning his shoulders in the soot.  "You 
surrender? Oh now dirty one.  At least we match now."  She laughed.  
She was having fun and enjoying time spend with him.  Something she 
had wanted to do for a long time, and that was spend time with him, 
doing anything.  At least they were having fun.
